---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const title = "Full Detail Fort Lauderdale | Mobile Service | Route95";
const description = "Complete mobile car detailing in Fort Lauderdale. Interior & exterior transformation. We come to you! Same-day appointments. Call 754-215-2272";

const parentCategory = {
  href: `${base}car-detailing-services-fort-lauderdale/`,
  title: "Car Detailing Services"
};
---

<ServiceLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  h1="Full Detail Fort Lauderdale"
  intro="A full detail is the complete interior and exterior transformation that makes your car look like it just rolled off the showroom floor."
  currentPage="/full-detail-fort-lauderdale/"
  parentCategory={parentCategory}
>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
      <section>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          A full detail goes far beyond a car wash. We address every surface inside and outâ€”cleaning, protecting, and restoring your vehicle to its best possible condition. This is the service for when you want your car to look truly exceptional.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          We bring our full detail service directly to your Fort Lauderdale location. Whether you're at home in Victoria Park or at your office near the Galleria, we arrive with all equipment and supplies needed for a complete transformation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Owner Gustavo Moya built Route95 around the idea that every vehicle deserves showroom-quality care. Our full detail delivers exactly that.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">How Much Does a Full Detail Cost in Fort Lauderdale?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>A full detail in Fort Lauderdale costs $200 to $400 depending on vehicle size and condition.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Sedans and coupes in good condition fall at the lower end. Larger vehicles like SUVs and trucks cost more due to increased surface area. Vehicles that haven't been detailed in a long time may need additional work, which affects pricing.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We provide an exact quote based on your specific vehicle and its current condition.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">How Long Does a Full Detail Take?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>A full detail takes 4 to 6 hours depending on vehicle size and how much work is needed.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We don't rush through a full detail. Every surface gets proper attention. Since we come to your location, you can go about your day while we work. Many clients schedule their detail during work hours and return to a transformed vehicle.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
