        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">A full detail is ideal for:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-2">
          <li>Before selling your vehicle (increases value significantly)</li>
          <li>After purchasing a used car (start fresh)</li>
          <li>Seasonal deep clean (we recommend twice yearly)</li>
          <li>Special occasions (weddings, photo shoots, car shows)</li>
          <li>After long road trips or extended neglect</li>
